commit.message: Bitcoin Swap Provider using locally using bitcoinjs-lib

Small mvp functionality fixes (#70)

* Add API provider

* use bitcoin rpc provider with ledger

* Remove bitcoin address from example

* Fix rebasing and enable end to end bitcoin swap

* Update metamask and ethereum rpc provider to new jsonrpc

* consistent method naming, add docsb

* Add find secret fn's + small refactor of MM sign and Ledger change amt (#71)

Add Bitcoin RPC provider (#65)

* add watch mode

* Add API provider

* use bitcoin rpc provider with ledger

* simplify isUsedAddress

* Remove bitcoin address from example

* Fix rebasing and enable end to end bitcoin swap

* consistent method naming, add docsb

* rename .rpc to .jsonrpc
